node.text:
GYM BUILT 💪🏼🍑 The 6 week booty building challenge starts in just TWO WEEKS!! @tammyhembrowfitness Guys you DO NOT want to miss this challenge 🙌🏼 This is the epitome of how I train to get the best booty building results possible.
What it includes:
💓Cash prizes from $4000 for first place
💓Full 6 week program with videos/descriptions
💓Weekly giveaways
💓 Constant support from our TammyFit team & community
💓Full access to the app for the duration- all meal plans, glute activations, yoga etc
-
It is now available for sign up within the Tammy Fit with limited spots available. LINK IN BIO let's gooo
